 Disk相比iFunbox，有如下优点：</p>\n<p><span></span></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.iappstoday.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/08/Screenshot20100817at05.13.04.png\"><img title=\"Screen shot 2010-08-17 at 涓嬪崍05.13.04\" src=\"http://www.iappstoday.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/08/Screenshot20100817at05.13.04_thumb.png\" border=\"0\" alt=\"Screen shot 2010-08-17 at 涓嬪崍05.13.04\" width=\"272\" height=\"244\" /></a><a href=\"http://www.iappstoday.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/08/Screenshot20100817at05.14.08.png\"><img title=\"Screen shot 2010-08-17 at 涓嬪崍05.14.08\" src=\"http://www.iappstoday.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/08/Screenshot20100817at05.14.08_thumb.png\" border=\"0\" alt=\"Screen shot 2010-08-17 at 涓嬪崍05.14.08\" width=\"210\" height=\"244\" /></a></p>\n<p>1.可以将你的iPhone/iPod Touch/iPad作为移动硬盘，显示在PC/Mac的文件管理器中，直接访问和执行操作，无需单独窗口。</p>\n<p>2.开机自动运行，极小化显示，只在系统托盘中显示一个小图标，平时根本看不到。</p>\n<p>3.限时正版授权，完全没有时间限制和广告。</p>\n<p>4.软件在设备端独立创建DCIM文件夹，支持iOS系统内的直接浏览。</p>\n<p>5.多设备协同工作，一次插入多台iDevice，均可以同时工作。</p>\n<p>而且，软件支持App的智能识别和传输，比如GoodReader/Stanza，用户都会在桌面上找到专门的图标，直接点击即可访问其中的数据。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.iappstoday.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/08/Screenshot20100817at05.15.07.png\"><img title=\"Screen shot 2010-08-17 at 涓嬪崍05.15.07\" src=\"http://www.iappstoday.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/08/Screenshot20100817at05.15.07_thumb.png\" border=\"0\" alt=\"Screen shot 2010-08-17 at 涓嬪崍05.15.07\" width=\"131\" height=\"133\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.iappstoday.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/08/Screenshot20100817at05.28.23.png\"><img title=\"Screen shot 2010-08-17 at 涓嬪崍05.28.23\" src=\"http://www.iappstoday.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/08/Screenshot20100817at05.28.23_thumb.png\" border=\"0\" alt=\"Screen shot 2010-08-17 at 涓嬪崍05.28.23\" width=\"126\" height=\"132\" /></a></p>\n<p>此外，针对越狱用户，Phone Disk可以自动识别，并支持访问Root目录（需要AFC2ADD），让文件传输更加方便。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.iappstoday.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/08/Untitled.png\"><img title=\"Untitled\" src=\"http://www.iappstoday.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/08/U